      <scopecontent id="aspace_322f40a389e873b92214c5a240fc4090">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of various published works of printing schools and departments of British colleges, dating from 1930 to 1984. The materials include monographic works on a variety of subjects, brochures, datebooks, keepsakes, etc., most of which were printed by students in fulfillment of academic requirements.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_1a9a1eaca296f73bf26e618eea9301fd">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged alphabetically by school. Where names of schools have changed over the years, the most recent name of each school represented in the collection is listed first, followed by previous names in parentheses.</p>  
      </arrangement>
